<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/diary_20220601_01.jpeg" alt="疯狂六一1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/diary_20220601_02.jpeg" alt="疯狂六一2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/diary_20220601_03.jpeg" alt="疯狂六一3"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/diary_20220601_04.jpeg" alt="疯狂六一4"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/diary_20220601_05.jpeg" alt="疯狂六一5"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/diary_20220601_06.jpeg" alt="疯狂六一6"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/diary_20220601_07.jpeg" alt="疯狂六一7"></p>
<iframe height="498" width="510" src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/video_20220601_03.mp4" frameborder="0" 'allowfullscreen'=""></iframe><br><iframe height="498" width="510" src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/202206/video_20220601_04.mp4" frameborder="0" 'allowfullscreen'=""></iframe>

]]></content>
    
